events.message:
[Depends] Miniupnpc 1.9.20160209

2016/01/24:
  Change miniwget to return HTTP status code
  Increments API_VERSION to 16

2016/01/22:
  Improve UPNPIGD_IsConnected() to check if WAN address is not private.
  Parse HTTP response status line in miniwget.c

events.body: Is there a changelog for miniupnp? I can't find relevant commits here: https://github.com/miniupnp/miniupnp/commits/miniupnpd_1_9

@jonasschnelli the changelog for miniupnpc is [here](http://miniupnp.tuxfamily.org/files/changelog.php?file=miniupnpc-1.9.20160209.tar.gz).
The changelogs for all other mini binaries can be found on this page http://miniupnp.tuxfamily.org/files/

This would be the approximate diff (approximately, as it's based on dates - miniupnpc doesn't tag releases):
https://github.com/miniupnp/miniupnp/compare/3c18a3ef029ff9acf3b2fb15774ebc7b24e2d1f6...81e0ca10df401e7d188da36f20e118f68ddbd590
ACK on the config.guess/sub. Those miniupnpc parsing changes are scary as always.
